# Tailwind v4 and theming

- Tailwind is imported via [app/globals.css](mdc:app/globals.css) using `@import "tailwindcss"`.
- Theme tokens are defined with `@theme inline` and CSS variables (see [app/globals.css](mdc:app/globals.css)).
- Prefer utility classes in `className`; avoid ad-hoc inline styles where utilities exist.
- Dark mode is driven via media query variables; respect `--background`/`--foreground`.
- No separate `tailwind.config.js` is required for basic usage in v4.
